{"type":"message","id":"53a84f07","parentId":"89ae8cd2","timestamp":"2026-05-22T12:36:52.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether I need to use browser control to do the influencer outreach, and is questioning whether the agent-browser skill can handle this. Let me reassure them that yes, browser automation is the right tool for this kind of task - navigating to pages, filling forms, clicking buttons, etc.\n\nThe user seems to be confirming that they will provide the necessary information (URL, process details, etc.) and is asking if browser control is indeed what I need to use.\n\nLet me clarify - yes, browser automation via the `browser` tool is exactly what's needed for this kind of task:\n1. Navigate to the outreach page\n2. Search/browse influencers\n3. Click to view profiles\n4. Fill in outreach forms\n5. Send messages/invitations\n\nThe agent-browser skill actually provides the instructions for using the browser tool effectively. The browser tool itself is what controls the web pages.\n\nI should reassure the user that this is the correct approach and that I can:\n1. Open the webpage in a browser\n2. Navigate, click, fill forms, and submit\n3. Do this on a daily schedule via cron\n\nLet me give them a clear confirmation.","thinkingSignature":"a0d7509738157a8d339e1661c6c617d78ae91bbdbda1ded6736ddd832ee588ec"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n是的，**必须通过浏览器控制**来完成达人邀约操作——这不是 API 能搞定的事情。\n\n你说的 `agent-browser` 就是我的浏览器自动化工具，完全可以做到：\n\n| 步骤 | 浏览器能做的 |\n|------|-------------|\n| 打开达人邀约页面 | ✅ 导航到指定URL |\n| 搜索/筛选达人 | ✅ 点击搜索框、填筛选条件 |\n| 查看达人资料 | ✅ 点击进入达人主页 |\n| 填写合作信息 | ✅ 填写表单字段 |\n| 发送邀约 | ✅ 点击发送按钮 |\n| 循环邀约下一个 | ✅ 重复以上流程 |\n\n**我现在的计划：**\n1. 你提供达人邀约页面的 **网址**\n2. 我用浏览器打开，手动走一遍流程，把每个步骤记下来\n3. 把这个流程固化成每日自动任务，每天定时跑\n\n所以现在**只需要你告诉我那个达人邀约页面的网址**，我来测试能不能自动化操作。🔗"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1505,"output":438,"cacheRead":44736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46679,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779453406069,"responseId":"065f80de3608123f808c7980618e657a"}}
